{"tid":1802024,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大埔超級城藍屍「星泰真味」凌晨遭爆玻璃擲燃燒彈","createTime":"2019-12-29T06:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T09:10:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f83eecc74d5f7cc090718104b0c09b83d54f7e51","tid":1802024,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/e3QEHDseJh9AyPzSSaTHqg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUzO2g9NjAzO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20191229a080518.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fe3QEHDseJh9AyPzSSaTHqg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUzO2g9NjAzO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20191229a080518.jpg&h=20dc6566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大埔超級城一間已打烊的泰式餐廳，凌晨懷疑遭人砸毀窗櫥玻璃後投擲燃燒彈起火，消防到場將火救熄，事件中無人受傷。警方正追緝6名涉案人士。<br />\n<br />\n現場為大埔安邦路3號大埔超級城C區，保安見到6人犯案後逃去。警員凌晨3時24分接報後到場，消防將火救熄，經初步調查相信起火原因有可疑。現場遺下玻璃瓶碎及易燃液體氣味。案件列縱火，交由大埔警區刑事調查隊第九隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n事件中無人受傷，毋須疏散。警方正追緝6人，他們案發時戴口罩，身穿深色上衣及深色長褲。"},{"pid":"b840ec0c0e196f4b1da8bc76083ab091d07691cf","tid":1802024,"uid":206811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f83eecc74d5f7cc090718104b0c09b83d54f7e51","tid":1802024,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/e3QEHDseJh9AyPzSSaTHqg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUzO2g9NjAzO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20191229a080518.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fe3QEHDseJh9AyPzSSaTHqg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUzO2g9NjAzO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20191229a080518.jpg&h=20dc6566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大埔超級城一間已打烊的泰式餐廳，凌晨懷疑遭人砸毀窗櫥玻璃後投擲燃燒彈起火，消防到場將火救熄，事件中無人受傷。警方正追緝6名涉案人士。<br />\n<br />\n現場為大埔安邦路3號